    • swapNeed

      private static boolean swapNeed(Appointment a1, Appointment a2, char key)
      Determines if the appointment needs to be swapped based on given key.
      Parameters:
      a1 - first appointment
      a2 - second appointment
      key - the key based on which they see if swap needs to occur, "D" for date, "P" for provider, "C" for county, "T" for timeslot, "p" patient
      Returns:
      true if appointment needs to be swapped, false otherwise
